<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行加、减法混合运算时，如果参与运算的数是接近整十、整百、整千......的数，可把他们当作“整数”来计算，然后再计算“零头数”。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">598-297-203=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 598-297-206</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=600-300-200-2+3-6</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=100-5</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=95</Run>
    </Paragraph>
 </FlowDocument>